For an Editorial Database, the total CD-ROM space must be configured
in terms of pages.

It is not critical and (for the sake of virtual updates) also
recommended to specify a bit larger than the physical size of CD-ROM.
For example, specify 1 GB per CD-ROM, i.e. 500.000 pages with the 
default page size of 2KB.

   -	This DB parameter cannot be changed after DB creation.
   -	Command Line Syntax :   rs=<size in pages>
